{
  "id": "6a10d854c7a13f0404f68a9f",
  "title": "相通主義",
  "created": 1779488855,
  "updated": 1780407969,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a10d854c7a13f0404f68a9f",
      "text": "相通主義",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779488855,
      "updated": 1779488855
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10dc260000000000836e64",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779489831,
      "updated": 1779489832
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10dc270000000000836e65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779489831,
      "updated": 1779489831
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d83c0000000000b8a052",
      "text": " [新現代思想]の一つ[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779488855,
      "updated": 1779488874
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d8700000000000b8a057",
      "text": "  英：channelism",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779488907,
      "updated": 1779488911
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d8520000000000b8a055",
      "text": "  [資本主義]と[共産主義]の止揚を目指したもの",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779488877,
      "updated": 1779489081
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d92e0000000000b8a061",
      "text": "   資本主義が無骨格動物、共産主義が外骨格動物なら、相通主義は内骨格動物（脊椎動物）への進化である",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489098,
      "updated": 1779489199
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1eda6e00000000003f4e97",
      "text": "   経済を内側から支える「骨」の部分を集中的に開発していくことが最大の公共の利益につながる国家の役割であるとする",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780406927,
      "updated": 1780407944
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d86b0000000000b8a056",
      "text": "  人・物・情報の相通性（channelity）を極限まで高めることを目指す",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779488902,
      "updated": 1779488981
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d8ba0000000000b8a058",
      "text": "   そのための技術を「[相通化技術]」と呼び、二つの具体的な技術アイデアがあって初めて成り立つ構想であった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779488981,
      "updated": 1780407969
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d8c20000000000b8a059",
      "text": "    二大相通化技術",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779488990,
      "updated": 1779489001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d8cd0000000000b8a05a",
      "text": "     [知機]（knower，知識機械）",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489001,
      "updated": 1780406919
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d8da0000000000b8a05b",
      "text": "      情報の相通化技術",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489013,
      "updated": 1779489021
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d9040000000000b8a05e",
      "text": "       [デルン]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489055,
      "updated": 1779489060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d90c0000000000b8a05f",
      "text": "        [デライト]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489063,
      "updated": 1779489069
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d8e10000000000b8a05c",
      "text": "     [万軌]（omnirail，万能軌道）",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489021,
      "updated": 1780406922
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d83d0000000000b8a053",
      "text": "      人と物の相通化技術",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779488857,
      "updated": 1779489054
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10da2b0000000000b8a069",
      "text": "  主要な社会保障手段として[ベーシックウェルカム]（基礎雇用保障）を提唱している",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489351,
      "updated": 1780407135
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d9250000000000b8a060",
      "text": "  もともと「疎通主義」と呼んでいたが、響きが良くないので「相通主義」に",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489089,
      "updated": 1779489245
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d9af0000000000b8a063",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779489227,
      "updated": 1779489227
    }
  ]
}